HEADWORD: Afflicting
<hw>Af*flict"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Grievously painful;
distressing; afflictive; <as>as, an <ex>afflicting</ex> event</as>. --
Af*flict"ing*ly, <xex>adv</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

